HEADWORD: Iconolatry
<hw>I`co*nol"a*try</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Iconolater</er>.]</ety> <def>The worship of images as symbols; --
distinguished from <contr>idolatry</contr>, the worship of images
themselves.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

